text: Sybaguasu subcarinatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1885. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Sybaguasu subcarinatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Beetles described in 1885 Category:Hemilophini
